name: createInternalTransferEntry

testSteps.description: Given that I'm logged in to 'Internal Transfer From Cash/Bank' page

children.description: When i open page from sidebar menu: {General Ledger,Internal Transfer}

testSteps.description: Then the 'Internal Transfer From Cash/Bank' page should show up
When I set the Currency to 'USD'
When I set the Amount to '1000'
When I set the Cost Center to 'MAN5000'
When I set the Line Reference to '11111'
When I click on 'Select Bank' button
Then the 'Select BANK Account' modal should show up
When I select first checkbox from 'Select Bank Account' modal
When I set the Payment Reference/Cheque Number to '11111'
When I click on Submit button
When I click on Continue button

title: Create internal transfer entry
